# Cybersecurity Mini Lab 🛡️

A beginner-friendly cybersecurity project with essential Python scripts for security learning.

## ⚙️ Features

- 🔐 SHA-256 password hashing
- 🔎 Basic port scanning (localhost)
- 🔓 Brute force password simulation

## 📂 Files

- `hash_generator.py` – Generates SHA-256 hash from input
- `port_scanner.py` – Scans common ports on 127.0.0.1
- `brute_force_demo.py` – Tests multiple password guesses

## 🧠 Educational Purpose

This mini lab is designed for learning and demonstration. It shows how simple security mechanisms work in practice.

## 🛠️ Technologies

- Python 3
- hashlib
- socket
- time

## 🚫 Disclaimer

**For educational use only. Do not use for unauthorized access or scanning public systems.**

